basis

Similar to base, with the difference that the import method of based module
is called. Requires Sub::Uplevel.

INSTALLATION

To install this module, run the following commands:

    perl Build.PL
    ./Build
    ./Build test
    ./Build install


SUPPORT AND DOCUMENTATION

After installing, you can find documentation for this module with the perldoc command.

    perldoc basis

You can also look for information at:

    Search CPAN
        http://search.cpan.org/dist/basis

    CPAN Request Tracker:
        http://rt.cpan.org/NoAuth/Bugs.html?Dist=basis

    AnnoCPAN, annotated CPAN documentation:
        http://annocpan.org/dist/basis

    CPAN Ratings:
        http://cpanratings.perl.org/d/basis

